ITT Corp said its long distanceunit is offering WATS telephone service for its customers.    The service is designed for customers with more than 500dlrs in monthly telephone bills, the company said.    The company said customers will save up to 15 pct over asimilar service offered by American Telephone and Telegraph Co&lt;T>. ITT is also waiving the 50 dlr per line installation feefor new or existing subscribers through March 31. Reuter&#3;